To install dependencies run 'npm install' on the terminal

To run the program on port 3000 run 'npm start'

sample api requests

for getting the rate with respest to the indian ruppee
1. http://localhost:3000/api/currencyRate/?currencyCode=ARS
2. http://localhost:3000/api/currencyRate/?currencyCode=MAD

sample output
{
    "rate": 0.135413,
    "currencyCode": "MAD"
}

for bitcoin data based on user provided currency code

1. http://localhost:3000/api/getData/?currencyCode=MAD
2. http://localhost:3000/api/getData/?currencyCode=ARS

sample output

{
    "btc": {
        "symbol": "btcinr",
        "baseAsset": "btc",
        "quoteAsset": "ARS",
        "openPrice": 3302695.790252,
        "lowPrice": 3051158.3000000003,
        "highPrice": 3340933.982947,
        "lastPrice": 3114830.589324,
        "volume": "12.32715",
        "bidPrice": 3110386.667,
        "askPrice": 3122639.759773,
        "at": 1663147489000
    }
}